# Python / GitHub Actions runtime

Use existing automation:

```powershell
py -m unittest discover tests
py bot_runner.py --dry-run
py settings_gui.py
py manage_rules.py validate
py manage_rules.py list
powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File install_start_menu_shortcut.ps1
```

The production bot runs through `.github/workflows/reddit-bot.yml`.
The master switch is `BOT_ENABLED`; keep disabled-by-default behavior unless the task is explicitly about enabling production.

The local settings GUI writes `.env`, which is gitignored.
Do not replace it with manual env editing when the GUI or scripts already cover the workflow.
